kpi_info.title: INTRA_MSC_GSM_TO_UMA_SUCC
kpi_info.use: Number of successful intra-MSC GSM-UMAhandovers. The trigger points for updating this counter are when HANDOVER COMPLETE message is received from UNC.

kpi_info.title: INTRA_MSC_GSM_TO_UMA_FAIL
kpi_info.use: handover failure due to timer expiry in MSC.

kpi_info.title: INTRA_MSC_GSM_TO_UMA_REEST
kpi_info.use: Number of successful re-establishmentsin failed intra-MSC GSM-UMA handovers. The counter is updated when an ASSIGNMENT COMPLETE MESSAGE is received after a handover failed.

kpi_info.title: INTRA_MSC_GSM_TO_UMA_DROP
kpi_info.use: Number of calls dropped due to failed intra-MSCGSM-UMA handovers. The counter is updated when a CLEAR REQUEST or an IU RELEASE REQUEST message is received from the attempted handover.
